@ENDNODE



@NODE "Guru.info"

 The 'Guru' drawer.
 ------------------

 This one was made for a small program called 'The Guru', which explains
 the complaints of our Amiga's spiritual teacher 8). Guess what's on that
 drawer? No, not a requester, it's a Guru!

@ENDNODE



@NODE "HandyDMS.dr.info"

 The 'HandyDMS' drawer.
 ----------------------

 Well... 'HandyDMS' is a GUI for 'DMS'. The drawer should now explain
