 The 'Help' drawer.
 ------------------

 You could use the 'Repair' drawer from @{"MagicWB" LINK "What is MagicWB 2.0?"} instead of this one but I
 don't like that one as a 'Help' drawer. This one looks more like a
 first-aid kit, thus it's more suitable.

